        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
          Roots of Tomorrow will not be held liable for any direct, indirect, or consequential damages arising from your use or inability to use our website or services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-600 text-canopy">5. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
          These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which Roots of Tomorrow operates. Any disputes arising from these terms will be resolved in the appropriate courts.
        </p>
