    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
      If you have any questions regarding these Terms of Service, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@rootsoftomorrow.org" class="text-leaf hover:underline">contact@rootsoftomorrow.org</a>.
